						<summary>

						<p>This is dated in Śārvari year, Āḍi 19, and is written in modern characters. It records a <hi rend="italic">sarvamānya</hi> gift of land by Bālaya-Nāyakkar to help in the maintenance of a <hi rend="italic">chattram</hi> established by Saśimuka-Mīnākshi-nāyakkar in front of the temple of Mīnākshi-Sundarēśvarasvāmi at Tiruvālavāy (Madurai). </p>						

						</summary>
